# Issues

This directory tracks defects and blockers discovered during implementation.

## Format

`ISSUE-NNN-kebab-slug.md` using the template in the project orchestrator spec.

## Status Values

OPEN | IN_PROGRESS | RESOLVED | CLOSED

## Rules

- Issue IDs are permanent — never delete issue files
- Every defect gets an issue before resolution
- Link issues from task files under `# Related Issues`

## Open Issues

None at project initialization.
